title: [CLIENT] Caitlyn Headhunter Skin
body: So I hopped into a match of team builder solo, and picked Cait. As I was looking through her skins something seemed off; Headhunter  Caitlyn (who I do not own) did not appear in her rotation of skins. I realize this is a pretty minor bug, but I thought I should still report it.

replies.body: Thanks for the heads up! We're investigating!

I've noticed this in multiple champions, but the ones I can specifically remember were all legacy/limited skins. It still confused me that I could view Victorious Janna, but not other skins that are no longer available. Is this a bug or meant to happen?
